events.text:
People don't even knock before falling down someone's sewer hole anymore, the town cryer was right times have changed.
Sorry? HA! Kind of impressive I've stayed on your back for so long considering you don't have a spine.
No ladder, have you tried just jumping higher? Guess this hole here is your best bet then. Time to challenge your inner monkey. You think it's inner Demon?
Thanks but I'm pretty certain it's monkey, maybe give up on wordplay and stick to swinging that sword of yours.
(press Q for heavy attack and E for light attack)
